        .footerColumnBody
          p
            | It is a priority for CBC to create a website that is accessible to all Canadians including people with visual, hearing, motor and cognitive challenges.
          p
            | Closed Captioning and Described Video is available for many CBC-TV shows offered on 
            a.footerLink.cbcWatch(href='https://watch.cbc.ca/') CBC Gem
            | .
          ul.footerList
            li.footerItem
              a.footerLink(href='https://www.cbc.ca/accessibility/') More about CBC Accessibility
            li.footerItem
              a.footerLink(href='https://www.cbc.ca/accessibility/feedback/') Accessibility Feedback
